# Environment variable templates
#
# This repository uses a separate .env file in each client package directory.
# Copy the appropriate template for your use case and fill your values:
#
#   Console:        cp packages/langgraph-fabric-console/.env.example packages/langgraph-fabric-console/.env
#   FastAPI server: cp packages/langgraph-fabric-api/.env.example packages/langgraph-fabric-api/.env
#   M365 adapter:   cp packages/langgraph-fabric-m365/.env.example packages/langgraph-fabric-m365/.env
#
# See the package-specific .env.example files for the full list of variables.
